        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"112165\">rss-bot</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/116290-rss/topic/Recent.20Commits.20to.20mathlib4.3Amaster/near/377318213\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/commit/8fe2ce366cdcf5d06ea7d8de708d81e7d4df8873\">feat(LinearAlgebra.Finsupp): add countable instance</a></strong> (<a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/5671\">mathlib4#5671</a>)</p>\n<p>Add the instance: </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">instance</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">ι</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Countable</span> <span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Countable</span> <span class=\"n\">ι</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">v</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ι</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Countable</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Submodule.span</span> <span class=\"n\">R</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Set.range</span> <span class=\"n\">v</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>which is needed to be able to apply Minkowski theorem to ℤ-lattices. This instance, in turn, uses the new instance:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">instance</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Countable</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Countable</span> <span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Countable</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"bp\">→₀</span> <span class=\"n\">M</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Authored-by: <a href=\"https://github.com/xroblot\">xroblot</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/commit/8fe2ce366cdcf5d06ea7d8de708d81e7d4df8873\">(commit)</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"488648\">@Xavier Roblot</span> I've recently added another proof of <code>Countable (α →₀ M)</code> in <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/5875\">#5875</a> (created after your PR, merged earlier). Could you please open a PR that deletes one of the proofs? Or should I do this?</p>",
